<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Urgent Lesson Request</h1>
    <h4>Another instructor had to cancel this previously confirmed lesson. If you're available, please confirm this lesson asap.</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Requester: <%= @lesson.requester.name %></li>
      <li>Date: <%= @lesson.date %></li>
      <li>Slot: <%= @lesson.slot %></li>
      <li>Location: <%= @lesson.location %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      To take the lesson, go to the lesson page below
      and click the 'Take It' button before another
      instructor beats you to it!
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= lesson_url(@lesson) %>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
